text: Elisabeth Gram (born 17 April 1996) is an Austrian freestyle skier. She competed in the 2018 Winter Olympics in the women's halfpipe. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Austrian female freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Austria Category:Competitors at the 2012 Winter Youth Olympics Category:People from Landeck District Category:Sportspeople from Tyrol (state) Category:Youth Olympic gold medalists for Austria
